title: Kodak Funsaver One Time Use Film Camera (2-pack)
description: If you're looking for a fun, easy way to take great pictures, indoors or out, the Kodak Fun Saver Single-Use Camera is a great choice.
Loaded with Kodak 800 speed, 27 exposure film for pictures with bright, vibrant colors.
With a 4 to 11.5-feet flash range. Must charge before every picture.
